Mineworkers Investment Co., which is
owned by a trust of  South Africa ’s National Union of
Mineworkers, may list in Johannesburg, Johannesburg’s Business
Day reported, citing the company’s Chief Executive Officer, Paul
Nkuna.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
